api_list.description: A Get Request to retrieve OSRS's personal hiscores's skills section from source URL: https://secure.runescape.com/m=hiscore_oldschool/overall
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://osrs2.p.rapidapi.com/personal-hiscores/skills/sweeteggcake"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "osrs2.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
